# Abay, Altai Republic

}}
Abay (; ) is a rural locality (a selo) in Ust-Koksinsky District, the Altai Republic, Russia. The population was 362 as of 2016. There are 4 streets.
Geography
Abay is located 52 km northwest of Ust-Koksa (the district's administrative centre) by road. Amur is the nearest rural locality.
